						<div class="postbody">Hey everyone.<br /><br />As you all know or should know by now.<br />The pal nes can't be modified to output ntsc.<br />But i recently thought to myself:<br />what if i overclock the pal cpu to get a similar game-speed as the ntsc nes?<br />Of course it will still output pal but at least the speed will be the ntsc like speed for all the slowed down games like castlevania.<br /><br />Would this be possible?<br /><br />Greets</div>

