					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">It won't work. You could fix the music pitch by overclocking but that's it. The VBlank interrupts will still happen at 50 Hz.<br /><br />If you overclock both the PPU and the CPU then the VBlank interrupts could happen at 60 Hz, resulting in a normal game speed, but then the video signal would be completely wrong, and very probably unusable.<br /><br />In other words : It is cheaper/simpler to buy a famicom <img src="./images/smilies/icon_smile.gif" alt=":)" title="Smile" /></div>

